items.title: Awesome Security
items.content_text:
### Network / IDS / IPS / Host IDS / Host IPS

*   [Zeek](https://zeek.org/) - Zeek is a powerful network analysis framework that is much different from the typical IDS you may know.
    *   [zeek2es (⭐35)](https://github.com/corelight/zeek2es) - An open source tool to convert Zeek logs to Elastic/OpenSearch.  You can also output pure JSON from Zeek's TSV logs!
